about.summary: PyPy is a Python interpreter and just-in-time compiler.

name: pypy2.7
raw_recipe:
{% set name = "pypy2.7" %}
{% set version = "5.10.0" %}
{% set hash = "c966124497ba8728654ce1161fa4c46b035ff30f289be70960f58292e5897cc8" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://bitbucket.org/squeaky/portable-pypy/downloads/pypy-5.10.0-linux_x86_64-portable.tar.bz2
  fn: {{ name|lower }}_{{ version }}.tar.bz2
  sha256: {{ hash }}


build:
    number: 0
    skip: True  # [win or osx]

requirements:
    run:
        - zlib
        - bzip2

test:
    commands:
        - pypy --help

about:
    home: http://pypy.org/
    license: MIT
    license_family: MIT
    license_file: LICENSE
    summary: PyPy is a Python interpreter and just-in-time compiler.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mictadlo

about.summary: PyPy is a Python interpreter and just-in-time compiler.
